No one use those useless Al'kobar spells, period. <br>
<br>
Yes, PoF is the best quad kite after 51 before 54 and is similar to COF from 34. It will nuke 4 at most.<br>
If u do single in 53, I would say u are slow, quad kite is the way to go in CS, almost every wiz and drood do that there except they are low lvl. Sometimes, u will see other classes hunting there, but they pull single only.<br>
Actually, it seems for me, using quad kite even use less mana than single since draught of fire hit lesser amt and use more mana totally to finish one wyvern.<br>
PoL is the greatest, 80% they will not resist it, 4 shots all 4 died in front of u, great feeling. PoFrost will get resisted sometimes though.<br>
<br>
One more thing, don't let LAG mob hit u, it is bad for me I got hit a little yesterday, boom, 1 to 2 secs , I am dead meat and need to find rezzer hard (off peak, and mostly no cleric will goto CS)<br>
